</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="78" pageNumber="79">The Russian and English texts vary somewhat from one another; the Russian is more comprehensive.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="78" pageNumber="79" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="78" pageNumber="79">
Southern Kazakhstan: paper-shales near Galkino (approximately 
<geoCoordinate degrees="42.15" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="555" value="42.15">42.15N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="70.02" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="555" value="70.02">70.02E</geoCoordinate>
), Chimkentskaya oblast district. Mesozoic: Upper Jurassic, probably Oxfordian.
</paragraph>
